{"tid":1845812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[一家人] 陳健波任 CEO 立橋保險　捐 500 萬給湖北抗疫","createTime":"2020-01-27T10:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T11:47:34.000Z","uid":297045,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b074bcb85828a73842fbef61dbaf6d25023f4e","tid":1845812,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"陳健波任 CEO 立橋保險 捐 500 萬助湖北抗疫<br />\n<br />\n曾以「大家一家人，唔可以隨便話停」反對封關抗疫的立法會保險界議員陳健波宣布，他擔任行政總裁的立橋保險集團，會捐出 1000 萬支援抗疫工作，其中 500 萬捐予香港志願機構，另外 500 萬捐給湖北省，支援武漢在內的抗疫工作；他又指希望港人齊心協力，「與內地及全球民眾一同擊退疫症。」<br />\n<br />\n陳健波又表示希望港府推出有效措施，令市民安心，包括確保口罩供應正常，不會有人炒賣抬價、確保公營醫療體系人手、裝備及設施足夠，視乎情況發放特別津貼予醫護人員、加強出入境的管制、檢疫、申報及隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chankinpor/posts/1267736990282802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchankinpor%2Fposts%2F1267736990282802&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=4bfe2fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chankinpor/posts/1267736990282802</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%99%B3%E5%81%A5%E6%B3%A2%E4%BB%BB-ceo-%E7%AB%8B%E6%A9%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA-%E6%8D%90-500-%E8%90%AC%E5%8A%A9%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BB%25BB-ceo-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA-%25E6%258D%2590-500-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%2F&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=6a7603f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BB%25BB-ceo-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25A9%258B%25